data.title: Dembele delights but frustrates in pivotal Barcelona win
data.description: Barcelona took advantage of an opening that Real Madrid left at the top of LaLiga and beat Atletico Madrid to move up.
data.snippet: Ousmane Dembele scores the lone goal to give Barcelona a 1-0 win. Stefan Savic and Ferran Torres also are sent off with red cards following an on-field scuffle....
